        "sender_full_name": "Formally Verified Waffle Maker",
        "timestamp": 1606201988
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>It's because if they were there then people would ask for epsilon-N definitions of other limits and then one sided limits and then the definition of a sequence tending to +infinity and etc etc, and then someone would realise that a beautiful way to do everything at once would be to use filters and then they'd all get changed to filters and we'd be back where we started</p>",
